Shongo Controller Command-Line Client

REQUIREMENTS

This client requires following Perl modules:
1) RPC::XML
2) XML::Twig

On Ubuntu/Debian system, the modules can be installed by
following command:

    sudo apt-get install librpc-xml-perl libxml-twig-perl

On other platform the modules can be installed for instance
by CPAN utility:

    cpan -i RPC::XML XML::Twig